<h1>Overlay</h1>

<p>Use the <code>overlay</code> tag to create a <a href="/api/havok/widget/Overlay.html">havok/widget/Overlay</a>. A widget designed to act as a Standby/Busy/Disable/Blocking widget to indicate a particular DOM node is processing and cannot be clicked on at this time.</p>
<p>An Overlay will always overlay it's parent dom node.</p>

